About Me

I'm Sakshi Kadu, a passionate Web Developer based in Nagpur with a focus on building interactive and user-friendly websites. I love turning ideas into functional, responsive, and aesthetic digital experiences.

My core tech stack includes HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, and Bootstrap. I’m constantly learning new technologies and working on projects that challenge me and expand my skills.

Whether it's building a portfolio website, developing a Chrome extension, or animating UI elements with GSAP, I always aim for performance, accessibility, and a smooth user experience.

When I’m not coding, you’ll find me exploring UI design, journaling thoughts, or contributing to developer communities.
